273
00:15:09,776 --> 00:15:13,613
Leave this place right now.

274
00:15:13,613 --> 00:15:14,714
Attack!

275
00:15:14,714 --> 00:15:19,419
♪

276
00:15:19,419 --> 00:15:23,489
Fighting is wrong.

277
00:15:23,489 --> 00:15:25,558
All right, pull back, men!

278
00:15:25,558 --> 00:15:29,729
♪

279
00:15:29,729 --> 00:15:30,830
No!

280
00:15:30,830 --> 00:15:37,069
♪

281
00:15:37,069 --> 00:15:39,338
Right, now get the disks!

282
00:15:39,338 --> 00:15:52,618
♪

283
00:15:52,618 --> 00:15:54,120
This can't be.

284
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:59,492
♪

285
00:16:03,863 --> 00:16:05,331
Let's get them!

286
00:16:05,331 --> 00:16:09,669
♪

287
00:16:09,669 --> 00:16:11,204
Golem's down!

288
00:16:11,204 --> 00:16:12,705
He's with us!

289
00:16:12,705 --> 00:16:15,308
You'd better let him
go, or you'll be sorry!

290
00:16:15,308 --> 00:16:16,576
Really?

291
00:16:16,576 --> 00:16:18,945
And who'll be sorry
when I'm done with you?

292
00:16:18,945 --> 00:16:21,347
(laughing)

293
00:16:21,347 --> 00:16:23,516
Stop it!

294
00:16:23,516 --> 00:16:25,117
You should be ashamed!

295
00:16:25,117 --> 00:16:27,687
There's nothing funny
about this at all.

296
00:16:27,687 --> 00:16:32,391
You are a bunch of
pitiful slime blobs!

297
00:16:32,391 --> 00:16:35,828
Huh, lovely speech, just lovely.

298
00:16:35,828 --> 00:16:38,965
Now, get him!

299
00:16:38,965 --> 00:16:40,967
(yelling)

300
00:16:40,967 --> 00:16:46,072
♪

301
00:16:46,072 --> 00:16:49,976
Genki!

302
00:16:49,976 --> 00:16:51,177
Mocchi, mocchi, mocchi!

303
00:16:51,177 --> 00:17:14,667
♪

304
00:17:14,667 --> 00:17:16,769
Golem.

305
00:17:16,769 --> 00:17:18,771
(shouting)

306
00:17:18,771 --> 00:17:27,580
♪

307
00:17:27,580 --> 00:17:29,649
You my friend, are resisting‐‐

308
00:17:29,649 --> 00:17:32,451
♪

309
00:17:32,451 --> 00:17:33,553
Oof!

310
00:17:33,553 --> 00:17:41,928
♪

311
00:17:41,928 --> 00:17:42,828
Captain?

312
00:17:42,828 --> 00:17:44,297
We're done for!

313
00:17:44,297 --> 00:18:01,914
♪

314
00:18:01,914 --> 00:18:03,683
Mercy!

315
00:18:03,683 --> 00:18:04,717
No, Golem!

316
00:18:04,717 --> 00:18:05,851
That's enough!

317
00:18:05,851 --> 00:18:08,354
♪

318
00:18:08,354 --> 00:18:10,356
(shouting)

319
00:18:10,356 --> 00:18:30,176
♪

320
00:18:30,176 --> 00:18:31,811
What's going on?

321
00:18:31,811 --> 00:18:32,845
Where are the jells?

322
00:18:32,845 --> 00:18:34,413
They're all gone, Golem.

323
00:18:34,413 --> 00:18:36,482
You made them lost monsters.

324
00:18:36,482 --> 00:18:52,965
♪

325
00:18:52,965 --> 00:18:55,735
I've done a terrible,
terrible thing.

326
00:18:55,735 --> 00:18:58,204
Lost monsters, more stones...

327
00:18:58,204 --> 00:19:25,765
♪

328
00:19:25,765 --> 00:19:30,870
Those flowers, each one is a
tear that you shed, isn't it?

329
00:19:30,870 --> 00:19:33,339
Chi.

330
00:19:33,339 --> 00:19:35,141
Come on, cheer up, Golem,

331
00:19:35,141 --> 00:19:40,613
The Phoenix will turn each of
these disks into a good monster.

332
00:19:40,613 --> 00:19:44,550
Right, it's an ancient
legend from my village.

333
00:19:44,550 --> 00:19:47,019
Of course, we have to
get the Phoenix, first.

334
00:19:47,019 --> 00:19:49,121
Come on, join us!

335
00:19:49,121 --> 00:20:10,710
♪

336
00:20:10,710 --> 00:20:13,112
(laughing)

337
00:20:13,112 --> 00:20:15,147
That's great!

338
00:20:15,147 --> 00:20:17,583
Keep it down!

339
00:20:17,583 --> 00:20:19,952
Well, you can call me Genki.

340
00:20:19,952 --> 00:20:21,353
My name is Holly.

341
00:20:21,353 --> 00:20:23,189
Suezo here.

342
00:20:23,189 --> 00:20:27,760
Mocchi!

343
00:20:27,760 --> 00:20:29,995
My name is Golem.

